---
// Benefits section component
---

<section id="beneficios" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900/50 to-purple-900/30">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        Tus beneficios exclusivos
      </h2>

    </div>
    
    <!-- Benefits Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Benefit 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-white/20 hover:border-green-400/50">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Crédito de libre inversión
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Destina tu dinero como quieras: paga tus deudas, invierte o úsalo en lo que más te importe.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Benefit 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-white/20 hover:border-green-400/50">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Trámite 100% Digital
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Realiza todo el proceso de tu préstamo desde cualquier computadora o dispositivo móvil, sin necesidad de desplazarte.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Benefit 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-white/20 hover:border-green-400/50">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Aunque tengas reportes en centrales de riesgo
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          ¿Estás reportado o no tienes historial crediticio? No importa. Creemos en segundas oportunidades y te ofrecemos préstamos sin necesidad de codeudores.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Benefit 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-white/20 hover:border-green-400/50">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Compra de cartera con tasa de interés preferencial
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          La solución a tus deudas comienza aquí. Reorganiza tus finanzas con la mejor tasa del mercado.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Benefit 5 -->
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-white/20 hover:border-green-400/50">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Sin importar tu edad
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Te apoyamos en cada etapa de tu vida. Accede a un préstamo, incluso hasta los 84 años, y sigue alcanzando tus metas.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Benefit 6 -->
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-white/20 hover:border-green-400/50">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Recibe tu aprobación el mismo día
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Con nuestro proceso ágil y sencillo, recibirás tu aprobación el mismo día. No esperes más para dar el primer paso hacia tu crédito.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>